data.description: Close to the Coleman Bridge! This 4 BR, 2.5 Bath home w/ a loft on the second floor sits on a 1/4 acre lot in Beckwith Farms. This home has an open floor plan, living room w/gas Fireplace, kitchen w/ stainless appliances, large island for extra counter and cooking space, & tons of cabinets. A spacious primary suite w/ private bathroom and walk-in closet. New LVP on entire 1st floor! And an attached 2 car garage completes this home.
